"Theme/Focus:  IoT Solutions for Commuters
 
Summary: 
Few things that everyone contends with yet finds a lot of pain around is commuting.  This could be on foot, on a bike, on motorcycles, public transportation, personal vehicle or airline (think management consultants or Intel employees).  How can IoT solutions (using the Edison platform) help solve major pain points?  We’ll explore through design thinking some of the issues that are faced by real live commuters and find innovative solutions that will be solved using IA.
